quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,52,"They are those whom God cursed them, and anyone cursed by God then you will never find a helper for him"
  4,53,Or do they have any share of the rule? In that case they will not give a tiny bit to the people
  4,54,"Or are they jealous of the people for what God gave them from His grace? We have given Abrahamâ€™s family the book and the wisdom, and we gave them a great kingdom"
  4,55,"Some of them believed in him and some of them turned away from him, and burning fire of hell is enough (for them)"
  4,56,"Those who disbelieved in Our signs, We will enter (and burn) them in a fire, every time their skins is roasted, We replace their skins with another skin so that they taste the punishment. God is powerful and wise"
  4,57,"And those who believed and did good works, We are going to admit them into gardens which rivers flow through them, remaining in there forever and ever. They have pure spouses in there, and We admit them into an abundant shade"
  4,58,"Indeed God orders you to return the trust to their owners, and when you judge between the people, judge with justice. Indeed what God advises you to it is excellent. God hears all and sees all"
  4,59,"You who believe, obey God and obey the messenger and those of you who are in charge of affairs (the authorities), but if you dispute about anything (with authorities), then return it to God and the messenger if you believe in God and the last day. This is better and has a better outcome"